[node name="Level7" type="Node3D"]
editor_description = "Room 07 — The Long Chain. No new mechanic: just 8 required objects spread along a 60m corridor instead of a handful in one room. Gear1/2/3 each auto-trigger the WireNode right after them (a real chain link), but the Vials still need a direct hit — so the player has to keep landing kicks the whole way down, and a bad one late in the corridor costs a long rewind or a long walk back. GREYBOX FIRST PASS — object spacing and corridor length are unverified numbers, expect to retune in-editor."

